### Finance Dashboard API — Test Suite
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client extension

# ─── Set your base URL ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@base = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken    = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_TOKEN
@analystToken  = REPLACE_WITH_ANALYST_TOKEN
@viewerToken   = REPLACE_WITH_VIEWER_TOKEN


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  HEALTH
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH — Login (run these first, copy tokens above)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Login as ADMIN → copy token to @adminToken
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@finance.dev",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### Login as ANALYST → copy token to @analystToken
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "analyst@finance.dev",
  "password": "Analyst@123"
}

###

### Login as VIEWER → copy token to @viewerToken
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "viewer@finance.dev",
  "password": "Viewer@123"
}

###

### Register a new user (open endpoint)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@finance.dev",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "role": "viewer"
}

###

### Get own profile (authenticated)
GET {{base}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ─── Validation Error — missing email ────────────────────
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "Admin@123"
}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  USERS — Admin only
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all users
GET {{base}}/api/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get single user (replace :id)
GET {{base}}/api/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update user role
PATCH {{base}}/api/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "analyst"
}

###

### Deactivate user
PATCH {{base}}/api/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}

###

### Delete user
DELETE {{base}}/api/users/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ─── RBAC: Viewer tries to list users → 403 ──────────────
GET {{base}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  FINANCIAL RECORDS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create record (admin)
POST {{base}}/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50000,
  "type": "income",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-01",
  "notes": "Monthly salary April 2026"
}

###

### List all records (any role)
GET {{base}}/api/records?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

###

### Filter by type
GET {{base}}/api/records?type=expense&category=Rent
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{base}}/api/records?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Search records
GET {{base}}/api/records?search=salary
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Get single record (replace :id)
GET {{base}}/api/records/REPLACE_WITH_RECORD_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

###

### Update record (admin)
PATCH {{base}}/api/records/REPLACE_WITH_RECORD_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 55000,
  "notes": "Updated salary amount"
}

###

### Soft delete record (admin)
DELETE {{base}}/api/records/REPLACE_WITH_RECORD_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ─── RBAC: Viewer tries to create record → 403 ────────────
POST {{base}}/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100,
  "type": "income",
  "category": "Test",
  "date": "2026-04-01"
}

###

### ─── Validation: negative amount → 422 ──────────────────
POST {{base}}/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -500,
  "type": "income",
  "category": "Test",
  "date": "2026-04-01"
}

###

### ─── Validation: invalid date → 422 ─────────────────────
POST {{base}}/api/records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100,
  "type": "income",
  "category": "Test",
  "date": "not-a-date"
}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  DASHBOARD
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Summary (analyst+)
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Category totals (analyst+)
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{analystToken}}

###

### Monthly trends (analyst+)
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/trends?period=monthly&limit=6
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Weekly trends
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/trends?period=weekly&limit=8
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Recent activity (all roles)
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/recent?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

###

### ─── RBAC: Viewer tries dashboard/summary → 403 ──────────
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}
